snippet.title: Doom 2: Junkfood 2 Wad Trailer
snippet.description:
Download: https://www.doomworld.com/forum/topic/138114

Junk Food 2 is a Boom compatible Speedmapping Community Project held in the Pacifist Paradise Discord Server. The basic premise was to make "Junk Food" slaughter (BFG spammy, high monster count maps) where not a lot of time is spent deliberating about layout/detailing/fight design/other things that can bog a mapper down. It's just good BFG fun.
